  title="What PISCES actually changes for retail investors"
  description="The UK's PISCES regime gives private-share trading a regulated home with intermittent auctions. What structured liquidity windows can do, what they can't, and why suitability still decides everything."
  category="Policy"
  meta="6 July 2026 · 9 min · By the Bundle team"
  nextLabel="The Academy: illiquidity, explained properly"
